  Version bump. Fix building with USE=doc or USE=test. Install README.txt.

  13 Apr 2010; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org>
  -htmlentities-4.1.0.ebuild, -htmlentities-4.2.0-r1.ebuild:
  Remove old versions.

