  htmlentities-4.2.0-r2.ebuild:
  Restore ~x86 keyword since the virtual is restored as well.

*htmlentities-4.2.0-r2 (15 Dec 2009)

  15 Dec 2009; Diego E. Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org>
